      <description>&lt;p&gt;For a long time I wanted to update my bio, I joined Grafana 2 years ago and I didn&amp;rsquo;t update yet&amp;hellip;&lt;em&gt;Good Ol&amp;rsquo; Obsolescence&lt;/em&gt; made the current version of Hugo be incompatible with the previous theme, so I had to update it.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This time I used &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/jpanther/congo&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;congo&lt;/a&gt; which has some nice features like dark mode. I also added a GitHub action to deploy the site to GitHub pages. Before I had two different repos, one for the source code and another for the generated site.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
